<h1 class="m-0">CustomCursor</h1>

<p>
  <a href="https://antonbobrov.github.io/vevet/classes/CustomCursor.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Docs</a>
  /
  <a href="https://github.com/antonbobrov/vevet-demo/blob/main/src/pages/custom-cursor/index.ts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Source Code</a>
